<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/daisyui@1.5.0/dist/full.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <title>Love Letter</title>
  <style>
    @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Shadows+Into+Light&display=swap');
    .handwritten {
      font-family: 'Shadows Into Light', cursive;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#f2e1bc] min-h-screen">
  <div class="flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen">
    <div class="relative bg-white w-4/5 md:w-1/2 lg:w-1/3 p-8 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
      <p class="handwritten text-lg text-[#4d1c0f] leading-relaxed">
        My Dearest [Name],
        <br><br>
        From the moment we met, I knew there was something special about you. Your warm smile, your laughter, and the way you light up every room you walk into. You have a magical touch that has captured my heart, and I am grateful every day for the love we share.
        <br><br>
        I cannot imagine a day without you by my side, supporting me, laughing with me, and being my rock through thick and thin. Your love has given me the strength to face the world with confidence and to become the person I am today.
        <br><br>
        Together, we have created countless memories and shared in each other's joys and sorrows. I look forward to many more years of love, laughter, and happiness with you, my love.
        <br><br>
        Forever yours,
        <br>
        [Your Name]
      </p>
      <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mt-4 -mr-4">
        <img src="paper-heart.png" alt="Paper Heart" />
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
